From {{inh|en|enm|laughen}}, {{m|enm|laghen}}, from (Anglian) {{inh|en|ang|hlæhhan}}, {{m|ang|hlehhan}}, (West Saxon) {{m|ang|hliehhan}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*hlahhjan}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*hlahjaną}}.
